text: 猪脚醋！ herbal bak kut teh. 莲藕排骨汤。木瓜银耳汤 and many more! Very good taste food!  And the soup is worth buying.  I am trying all the soup and so far, papaya soup is full of ingredients! Then the lotus soup is very tasteful.
Lotus root & peanut w/ pork rib soup is very tasty and delicious. Pork is tender too.

Food are fresh, soup are good.  Variety is big too. Definitely worth visiting. Even the radish scallop soup have a whole piece scallop. And the papaya soup is full of ingredients.  Lotus peanut soup is great too. I am going through the whole list.

Order from DinDinn app, SMS sent and saying food is ready to collect. Come and wait for 15 mins still not ready. The lady’s attitude is so rude and ask me to cancel the order if dun want. It’s no way to cancel coz its already in collection stage! She pass same order to other customer who was queueing after me, just ignoring me totally. Not recommended and pls be careful when you deal with this lady.

Long queue time to prepare
But food is nice
